    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/a3a8ceeffa2706bca4969a54e453f209.poster.avif?t=1768043803\" width=790 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/a3a8ceeffa2706bca4969a54e453f209.webm?t=1768043803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/a3a8ceeffa2706bca4969a54e453f209.mp4?t=1768043803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>作为一个强硬、不妥协的侦探，步入90年代初的大阪，来到<strong>COP BASTARD</strong>﻿——一款经典的快节奏走廊射击游戏，直截了当地进入战斗。没有谜题，没有特权，没有升级，决不浪费时间在花哨的机制上。只有受90年代硬派动作电影启发的原始、不懈的动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/b41217cd0e535d85ea7f0eb2f64681a1.poster.avif?t=1768043803\" width=790 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/b41217cd0e535d85ea7f0eb2f64681a1.webm?t=1768043803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/b41217cd0e535d85ea7f0eb2f64681a1.mp4?t=1768043803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在狭窄紧凑的走廊中穿梭，面对无尽的暴走族浪潮，每一枪都至关重要，生存取决于敏捷的反射和胆量。使用残酷的武器库，甚至向敌人脸上吐唾沫以彰显你的统治力。此游戏专为喜欢纯粹、不掺杂任何元素的老派射击游戏玩家量身打造：不准星射击，不升级角色，只为纯粹的射击狂热。如果你渴望高强度的走廊型FPS，COP BASTARD﻿绝对能满足你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/ba31fb7cd2e729036583cf39213a7a9d.poster.avif?t=1768043803\" width=790 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/ba31fb7cd2e729036583cf39213a7a9d.webm?t=1768043803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174740/extras/ba31fb7cd2e729036583cf39213a7a9d.mp4?t=1768043803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏使用现代引擎打造，但充满复古氛围，带你进入一个充满血腥、震撼音乐和混乱战斗的沉浸式世界。准备好奔跑、射击并在犯罪地下世界中吐口水吧——别指望有停歇的残酷乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
